Budgie Desktop is the default desktop on the Solus Linux distrubution and is a fantastic desktop. It can also be installed on other operating systems. This post looks at how to install the Budgie desktop on Opensuse Tumbleweed . It assumes that you have downloaded the ISO and installed on a USB using, for example, Etcher .
Installing Opensuse Tumbleweed The steps to installing Opensuse Tumbleweed from your USB:
On the first screen select &ldquo;Installation&rdquo;
